cmake_minimum_required(VERSION 3.5)

project(webrtc_video_coding__packet_buffer)

# Check if the major CMakeLists.txt file has correctly set
# the ANDROID_ROOT directory.
if (IS_DIRECTORY ${ANDROID_ROOT})
    message(STATUS "${PROJECT_NAME}, has been set android root")
else ()
    if (IS_DIRECTORY ${BUILD_NATIVE_ROOT})
        message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, set ANDROID_ROOT via BUILD_NATIVE_ROOT=${BUILD_NATIVE_ROOT}")
        set(ANDROID_ROOT ${BUILD_NATIVE_ROOT})
        set(OUT_INTERMEDIATES_ROOT ${ANDROID_ROOT}/out/soong/.intermediates)
    else ()
        message(FATAL_ERROR "${PROJECT_NAME}, ANDROID_ROOT was NULL")
    endif ()
endif ()

set(SOURCE_FILES "")
foreach (file ${FILES})
    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

if (NOT SOURCE_FILES)
    message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, source files not exist")
else ()
    add_library(webrtc_video_coding__packet_buffer SHARED ${SOURCE_FILES})

    target_include_directories(webrtc_video_coding__packet_buffer
            PUBLIC
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/crc32c/src/include
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/abseil-cpp
    )

    # Add c/c++ flags
    target_compile_options(webrtc_video_coding__packet_buffer PRIVATE
            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0
    )

    target_link_libraries(webrtc_video_coding__packet_buffer
            libaom
            libaom
            libc++_static
            libc++_static
            libc++demangle
            libc
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal
            libcrypto
            libcrypto
            libdl
            libevent
            libevent
            libm
            libopus
            libopus
            libpffft
            libpffft
            libprotobuf-cpp-full
            libprotobuf-cpp-full
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libsrtp2
            libssl
            libssl
            libvpx
            libvpx
            libwebrtc_absl_headers
            libyuv
            libyuv
            rnnoise_rnn_vad
            webrtc_api__rtp_packet_info
            webrtc_common_video__common_video
            webrtc_containers__flat_containers_internal
            webrtc_rtc_base__checks
            webrtc_rtc_base__copy_on_write_buffer
            webrtc_rtc_base__logging
            webrtc_rtc_base__platform_thread_types
            webrtc_rtc_base__rtc_event
            webrtc_rtc_base__rtc_numerics
            webrtc_rtc_base__socket
            webrtc_rtc_base__zero_memory
            webrtc_rtp_rtcp__rtp_rtcp_format
            webrtc_rtp_rtcp__rtp_video_header

endif ()

set(SOURCE_FILES "")
foreach (file ${FILES})
    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

if (NOT SOURCE_FILES)
    message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, source files not exist")
else ()
    add_library(webrtc_video_capture__video_capture_module SHARED ${SOURCE_FILES})

    target_include_directories(webrtc_video_capture__video_capture_module
            PUBLIC
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/crc32c/src/include
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/abseil-cpp
    )

    # Add c/c++ flags
    target_compile_options(webrtc_video_capture__video_capture_module PRIVATE
            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0
    )

            libaom

    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

            -Wextra

set(SOURCE_FILES "")
foreach (file ${FILES})
    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

if (NOT SOURCE_FILES)
    message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, source files not exist")
else ()
    add_library(webrtc_config__streams_config SHARED ${SOURCE_FILES})

    target_include_directories(webrtc_config__streams_config
            PUBLIC
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/crc32c/src/include
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/abseil-cpp
    )

    # Add c/c++ flags
    target_compile_options(webrtc_config__streams_config PRIVATE
            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0
    )

    target_link_libraries(webrtc_config__streams_config
            libaom
            libaom
            libc++_static
            libc++_static
            libc++demangle
            libc
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal
            libcrypto
            libcrypto
            libdl
            libevent
            libevent
            libm
            libopus
            libopus
            libpffft
            libpffft
            libprotobuf-cpp-full
            libprotobuf-cpp-full
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libsrtp2
            libssl
            libssl
            libvpx
            libvpx
            libwebrtc_absl_headers
            libyuv
            libyuv
            rnnoise_rnn_vad
            webrtc_adaptation__resource_adaptation
            webrtc_agc2__cpu_features
            webrtc_api__media_stream_interface
            webrtc_api__rtc_error
            webrtc_api__rtp_headers
            webrtc_api__rtp_packet_info
            webrtc_api__rtp_parameters
            webrtc_api__rtp_sender_interface
            webrtc_audio__audio_frame_api
            webrtc_audio_codecs__audio_codecs_api
            webrtc_audio_device__audio_device_impl
            webrtc_audio_processing__api
            webrtc_audio_processing__apm_logging
            webrtc_call__rtp_interfaces
            webrtc_config__encoder_config
            webrtc_containers__flat_containers_internal
            webrtc_experiments__field_trial_parser

            webrtc_experiments__normalize_simulcast_size_experiment

    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

if (NOT SOURCE_FILES)
    message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, source files not exist")
else ()
    add_library(webrtc_goog_cc__link_capacity_estimator SHARED ${SOURCE_FILES})

    target_include_directories(webrtc_goog_cc__link_capacity_estimator
            PUBLIC
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/crc32c/src/include
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/abseil-cpp
    )

    # Add c/c++ flags
    target_compile_options(webrtc_goog_cc__link_capacity_estimator PRIVATE
            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0
    )

    target_link_libraries(webrtc_goog_cc__link_capacity_estimator
            libaom
            libaom
            libc++_static
            libc++_static
            libc++demangle
            libc
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal
            libcrypto
            libcrypto
            libdl
            libevent
            libevent
            libm
            libopus
            libopus
            libpffft
            libpffft
            libprotobuf-cpp-full
            libprotobuf-cpp-full
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libsrtp2
            libssl
            libssl
            libvpx
            libvpx
            libwebrtc_absl_headers
            libyuv
            libyuv
            rnnoise_rnn_vad
            webrtc_rtc_base__checks
            webrtc_units__data_rate
            libc
            libdl
            libm
    )
endif ()

            PUBLIC

            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/crc32c/src/include
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/abseil-cpp
    )

    target_compile_options(webrtc_rtc_base__audio_format_to_string PRIVATE
            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0
    )

            libaom

    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

    message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, source files not exist")

    target_include_directories(webrtc_crypto__options
            PUBLIC
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/crc32c/src/include
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/abseil-cpp
    )

    # Add c/c++ flags
    target_compile_options(webrtc_crypto__options PRIVATE
            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0
    )

    target_link_libraries(webrtc_crypto__options
            libaom
            libaom
            libc++_static
            libc++_static
            libc++demangle
            libc
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.builtins

            libaom

set(SOURCE_FILES "")
foreach (file ${FILES})
    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

if (NOT SOURCE_FILES)
    message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, source files not exist")
else ()
    add_library(webrtc_pc__ice_server_parsing SHARED ${SOURCE_FILES})

    target_include_directories(webrtc_pc__ice_server_parsing
            PUBLIC
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/crc32c/src/include
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/abseil-cpp
    )

    # Add c/c++ flags
    target_compile_options(webrtc_pc__ice_server_parsing PRIVATE
            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0
    )

    target_link_libraries(webrtc_pc__ice_server_parsing
            libaom
            libaom
            libc++_static
            libc++_static
            libc++demangle
            libc
            libclang_rt.builtins

            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libsrtp2
            libssl
            libssl
            libvpx
            libvpx
            libwebrtc_absl_headers
            libyuv
            libyuv
            rnnoise_rnn_vad
            webrtc_agc2__cpu_features
            webrtc_api__libjingle_peerconnection_api
            webrtc_api__media_stream_interface
            webrtc_api__rtc_error
            webrtc_api__rtp_headers
            webrtc_api__rtp_packet_info
            webrtc_api__rtp_parameters
            webrtc_audio__audio_frame_api
            webrtc_audio_codecs__audio_codecs_api

            webrtc_audio_processing__api
            webrtc_audio_processing__apm_logging
            webrtc_call__rtp_interfaces
            webrtc_containers__flat_containers_internal

set(SOURCE_FILES "")
foreach (file ${FILES})
    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

    message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, source files not exist")
else ()

            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0

            libaom

set(SOURCE_FILES "")
foreach (file ${FILES})
    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

if (NOT SOURCE_FILES)
    message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, source files not exist")
else ()
    add_library(webrtc_pc__video_rtp_track_source SHARED ${SOURCE_FILES})

    target_include_directories(webrtc_pc__video_rtp_track_source
            PUBLIC
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/crc32c/src/include
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/abseil-cpp
    )

    # Add c/c++ flags
    target_compile_options(webrtc_pc__video_rtp_track_source PRIVATE
            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0
    )

    target_link_libraries(webrtc_pc__video_rtp_track_source
            libaom
            libaom
            libc++_static
            libc++_static
            libc++demangle
            libc
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal

            libcrypto
            libdl
            libevent

            libm
            libopus
            libopus
            libpffft
            libpffft

            libprotobuf-cpp-full
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libsrtp2
            libssl
            libssl
            libvpx
            libvpx
            libwebrtc_absl_headers
            libyuv
            libyuv
            rnnoise_rnn_vad
            webrtc_agc2__cpu_features
            webrtc_api__media_stream_interface
            webrtc_api__rtc_error
            webrtc_api__rtp_headers
            webrtc_api__rtp_packet_info
            webrtc_api__rtp_parameters
            webrtc_audio__audio_frame_api
            webrtc_audio_codecs__audio_codecs_api
            webrtc_audio_device__audio_device_impl
            webrtc_audio_processing__api
            webrtc_audio_processing__apm_logging
            webrtc_containers__flat_containers_internal
            webrtc_media__rtc_media_base

set(SOURCE_FILES "")
foreach (file ${FILES})
    if (EXISTS ${file})
        list(APPEND SOURCE_FILES ${file})
    endif ()
endforeach ()

if (NOT SOURCE_FILES)
    message(WARNING "${PROJECT_NAME}, source files not exist")
else ()
    add_library(webrtc_rx__reassembly_queue SHARED ${SOURCE_FILES})

    target_include_directories(webrtc_rx__reassembly_queue
            PUBLIC
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/webrtc
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/crc32c/src/include
            ${ANDROID_ROOT}/external/webrtc/third_party/abseil-cpp
    )

    # Add c/c++ flags
    target_compile_options(webrtc_rx__reassembly_queue PRIVATE
            -Wextra
            -Wno-unused-parameter
            -DWEBRTC_APM_DEBUG_DUMP=0
    )

    target_link_libraries(webrtc_rx__reassembly_queue
            libaom
            libaom
            libc++_static
            libc++_static
            libc++demangle
            libc
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.builtins
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal
            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal
            libcrypto
            libcrypto
            libdl
            libevent
            libevent
            libm
            libopus
            libopus
            libpffft
            libpffft
            libprotobuf-cpp-full
            libprotobuf-cpp-full
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libprotobuf-cpp-lite
            libsrtp2
            libssl
            libssl
            libvpx
            libvpx
            libwebrtc_absl_headers
            libyuv
            libyuv
            rnnoise_rnn_vad
            webrtc_containers__flat_containers_internal
            webrtc_packet__chunk
            webrtc_packet__parameter
            webrtc_rtc_base__checks
            webrtc_rtc_base__logging
            webrtc_rtc_base__platform_thread_types
            webrtc_rtc_base__rtc_event
            webrtc_rtc_base__socket
            webrtc_rtc_base__stringutils
            webrtc_rtc_base__zero_memory
            webrtc_rx__interleaved_reassembly_streams
            webrtc_rx__traditional_reassembly_streams
            webrtc_synchronization__sequence_checker_internal
            webrtc_synchronization__yield
            webrtc_task_queue__task_queue
            webrtc_units__time_delta
            libc
            libdl
            libm
    )
endif ()
